</svg> <h2 class="h4 leading-none uppercase text-balance split-heading max-w-256 dark:text-white text-right"> Take Your Ideas to the Next Level on Avalanche </h2> </div> <div class="flex flex-row items-start justify-start self-start lg:row-start-1 lg:col-start-1 justify-self-start"> <p class="split-text sm:text-balance">Avalanche offers a vast ecosystem of support for builders, from incubators and grant programs, to developer community calls and IRL hackathons.</p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="group/section animate-in-view relative w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-[0.75fr_auto] lg:[.visible&]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] transition-all duration-0 [.visible&]:duration-2000 ease-out-quart place-items-stretch px-md py-2xl lg:pl-3xl lg:pr-md lg:py-2xl rounded-4xl"> <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-4xl overflow-hidden"> <img src="/_astro/grants.gNp6OnIY_Z2q34vE.webp?dpl=dpl_FktV9TCgYa7QfpLGwEwEDv6yVhv5" alt="grants background" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="auto" width="2560" height="1440" class="w-full h-full object-cover"> </div> <div class="relative z-[1] p-md lg:pr-2xl flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-xl fill-black/50 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl border border-red"> <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-start justify-start gap-base"> <h2 class="h5 uppercase text-white text-balance sm:max-w-[30ch]">Codebase</h2> <p class="text-white sm:text-balance sm:max-w-[50ch]"> Codebase by Avalanche® is home to Avalanche’s Builder Support Programs—providing developers with incubators, innovation labs, hackathons, and hands-on resources all year long. </p> </div> <a class="group/button button arrow red-light !stroke-transparent w-full sm:w-auto" href="https://build.avax.network/codebase" target="_blank"> <wm-shape id="button" rounded="clamp(0.625rem, 0.196rem + 0.67vw, 1rem)" rounded-mobile="clamp(0.875rem, 0.803rem + 0.309vw, 1rem)" corner-rounded="clamp(0.25rem, 0.107rem + 0.223vw, 0.375rem)" corner-rounded-mobile="cl